ill) &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;2—Telekinesis Ray: range 8; &lt;u&gt;+17 vs. Fortitude&lt;/u&gt;; the target slides 4 squares.&lt;/p&gt;]]; the target slides 4 squares.</p><p>3—Fear Ray (Fear): range 8; [[/roll 1d20+17[ vs. Will]#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;➶ &lt;b&gt;Eye Rays&lt;/b&gt; (standard, at-will) &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;3—Fear Ray (Fear): range 8; &lt;u&gt;+17 vs. Will&lt;/u&gt;; the target moves its speed away from the eye of flame by the safest route possible and takes a -2 penalty to attack rolls (save ends)&lt;/p&gt;]]; the target moves its speed away from the eye of flame by the safest route possible and takes a -2 penalty to attack rolls (save ends)</p></tr></td><tr><td><h4><b>Minor</b></h4></td></tr><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;➶ &lt;b&gt;Central Eye&lt;/b&gt; (minor, at-will) &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ranged 8; the target gains vulnerable 10 fire, and any attack that deals fire damage to the target also deals ongoing 5 fire damage (save ends both).&lt;/p&gt;]] ➶ <b>Central Eye</b> (minor, at-will) </p><p>Ranged 8; the target gains vulnerable 10 fire, and any attack that deals fire damage to the target also deals ongoing 5 fire damage (save ends both).</p></tr></td><tr><td><h4><b>-</b></h4></td></tr><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;ᗕ &lt;b&gt;Fiery Burst&lt;/b&gt; ( when first bloodied and again when the eye of flame is reduced to 0 hit points, ) ✦ &lt;b&gt;Fire&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Close burst 2; +17 vs Reflex; 2d8+6 fire damage. &lt;/p&gt;]] ᗕ <b>Fiery Burst</b> ( when first bloodied and again when the eye of flame is reduced to 0 hit points, ) ✦ <b>Fire</b></p><p>Close burst 2; [[/roll 1d20+17[ vs Reflex]#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;ᗕ &lt;b&gt;Fiery Burst&lt;/b&gt; ( when first bloodied and again when the eye of flame is reduce